text: Norveig Karlsen (16 May 1922 – 9 March 1993) was a Norwegian artistic gymnast, born in Moss. She competed in gymnastics at the 1952 Summer Olympics in Helsinki. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1922 births Category:1993 deaths Category:People from Moss, Norway Category:Norwegian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Norway Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics
